"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1932519-piers-morgan-paris-olympic-games-complaint\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Piers Morganhas sparked backlash after he commented about Keely Hodgkinson winning gold at the 800m final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The middle distance runner won Team GB's first gold of theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 138, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999656367896, \"rank\": 3.4355348802549434e-08, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the 22-year old sprinted to victory, Piers took to X to re-share an old tweet he posted in 2021 when Keely won silver during the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He originally wrote: \\\"I am sorry that facts make you vomit.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Self-evidently, if you do not win a race, you lose it.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Keeley lost to someone the same age as her.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But great to see her break the British record and I hope she now works even harder & wins Gold at Paris in 2024.\\\"\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 528, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999999667661547, \"rank\": 3.322628302155856e-08, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}, {\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999994301561, \"rank\": 5.69855781360182e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following Keely's win, Piers then congratulated her and said: \\\" This aged well.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congrats@keelyhodgkinson- you took my advice and won,\\\" with added medal and clapping hands emojis.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of his followers have slammed the journalist in the comments section, with many describing him as \\\"shameful\\\" and told him to \\\"stop taking credit for her.\\\"\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:BBC's Jessica Ennis-Hill in tears as she makes heartbreaking family confession    One person said online: \\\"Will you stop claiming credit for every gold medal someone wins in the Olympics!\\\"\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9972919606457598, \"rank\": 0.0021123683441898414, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 969, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A second fan also wrote: \\\"Always making other people's success somehow about you.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shameless attention seeking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A third person typed: \\\"Love that she won, but sometimes Piers you can be completely moronic.\\\"\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fourth said: \\\"Your advice?\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your ego is out of control.\\\"\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After her sensational victory, Keely said: \\\"That was absolutely incredible.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have worked so hard over the last year and you could see how much it meant to me as I crossed the line.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not believe I have finally done it.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means so much to me.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:GMB's Kate Garraway halts show for 'breaking news announcement' about co-star  Do not miss:Emmerdale legend 'so proud' of co-star after 'tough days' on set  Do not miss:Coronation Street icon returns to cobbles after making dramatic exit  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\", \"score\": 0.999198499815389, \"rank\": 0.0008021431025623902, \"text\": \"GMB\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gamma-Hydroxybutyric_acid\"}, {\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 169