es\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have seen all the support from home, I have seen people messaging me and I have not got back to everyone yet but I will do and I have seen it all.\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It could not feel more amazing to that have support.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am super happy to bring it home for everyone.\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not just me, it's a whole team effort and they know who they are.\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is our gold medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3187, \"end\": 3200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.769859141777002e-23, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3236, \"end\": 3249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.769859141777002e-23, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"